definitions.definition: Self-referential ; structured analogously (structured by relationships), but at a higher level.
examples: Suppose you have a genie that grants you three wishes. If you wish for infinite wishes, that is a meta wish.
Suppose you have a homework task where you need to edit a wiki page and upload a screenshot of this entry underneath the word meta as an example of what meta is.

definitions.definition: Prominent in the metagame; effective and frequently used in competitive gameplay.
examples: I don't think the character will be meta even with the recent buffs.

main_definition: ( informal ) Self-referential ; structured analogously (structured by relationships), but at a higher level.
secondary_definitions: ( video games ) Prominent in the metagame; effective and frequently used in competitive gameplay.
